Sure, here are some example sentences in Serbian that use the word "klark" (кларк) in different forms and positions:

1. *Klark* je omiljeni junak u mnogim naučnofantastičnim romanima. (Clark is a favorite character in many science fiction novels.)
2. Daj mi ovaj *klark* za bušenje rupa. (Give me this drill bit for making holes.)
3. *Klarkov* posao je da vodi računa o održavanju mašina u fabrici. (Clark's job is to take care of machine maintenance in the factory.)
4. Da li si videla ovu novu *klark* mašinu? (Have you seen this new forklift machine?)
5. *Klark* se obično koristi za podizanje i premeštanje teških tereta. (A forklift is typically used for lifting and moving heavy loads.)
6. Naš šef je naredio da se nabavi novi *klark* za skladište. (Our boss ordered to buy a new forklift for the warehouse.)
7. *Klarkova* ideja za unapređenje proizvodnje je naišla na odobravanje direktora. (Clark's idea for improving production has been approved by the director.)
8. *Klark* je bio jedan od prvih naučnika koji su proučavali elektromagnetizam. (Clark was one of the first scientists to study electromagnetism.)

I hope these examples help!